PrecisAuthority to enter into an AGREEMENT with the Province of NEW BRUNSWICK which provides for the leasing to the Province, for a term of forty-nine (49) years, of an additional small piece of land (22'x 27') situate at the FREDERICTON RESEARCH STATION in the City of Fredericton, New Brunswick, which is to be used as the site for the construction of a chemical storage building.
